sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Usuario
    participant C as Cliente React
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant S as Community Service
    participant K as Keycloak
    participant O as ONNX Runtime
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis

    U->>C: 1. Escribe título, contenido y etiquetas
    U->>C: 2. Opcional: sube imagen
    
    C->>C: 3. Validar contenido (mínimo 10 caracteres)
    
    C->>G: 4. POST /community/posts
    Note over C,G: Authorization: Bearer {token}
    Note over C,G: {title, content, tags, imageUrl (base64 optional)}
    
    G->>S: 5. Proxy → /community/posts
    
    S->>K: 6. Introspect token (verifyToken)
    K-->>S: userInfo (postgresId, role, email)
    
    alt Token inválido
        S-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
        C-->>U: Mostrar "Sesión expirada"
    else Token válido
    
        Note over S: Preparar texto para embedding: title + content + tags
        
        S->>O: 7. POST /embed
        Note over S,O: {texts: ["título + contenido + tags"]}
        
        O->>O: 8. Tokenizar texto (BERT WordPiece)
        O->>O: 9. Inferencia ONNX (all-MiniLM-L6-v2)
        O-->>S: 10. embedding (384 dimensiones)
        
        alt Imagen en base64
            S->>S: 11. Subir imagen a Cloudinary
            Note over S: Generar firma SHA256
            S-->>S: imageUrl
        end
        
        S->>P: 12. INSERT INTO posts (user_id, title, content, tags, embedding, image_url)
        P-->>S: postId, created_at
        
        S->>R: 13. DEL community:posts:list:*
        S->>R: 14. DEL community:personalized:feed:{userId}
        S->>R: 15. DEL community:trending:posts:*
        Note over S,R: Invalidar cachés
        
        S-->>C: 16. 201 Created (postId, message)
        C-->>U: 17. Mostrar post creado exitosamente
    end